description: Fortalecimiento de las Capacidades de Gestión para la Gobernabilidad Democrática (SIGOB)

subproject.description: The Regional Project aims to develop the management capacities of high level authorities in charge of executive, legislative and judiciary powers in eleven Latin American countries to improve transparency, efficiency and efficacy of public institutions and their capacity to deliver services to their citizens. The countries in which the project could be executed are: Argentina, Uruguay, Chile, Brazil, Bolivia, Perú, Colombia, Panamá, Guatemala, El Salvador, México and Dominican Republic. The SIGOB regional project is implementing various systems in different countries, achieving the objective of capacity building.
